            <section xml:id="df/d6b/interface_modular_1_1_interfaces_1_1_service_1a7749758a4f5d2a71ba46116f9df7994d">
                <title>request ($serviceName, $data, $options=null, $requester=null)</title> <emphasis></emphasis>
                
<para>Make a request of a service, which generally calls request by extensions on Request extensions added to the service. <link linkend="df/d6b/interface_modular_1_1_interfaces_1_1_service">Service</link> request extensions should only do something with the request if the serviceName requested matches their own serviceName (which is generally their class name).</para>

<para>
                <formalpara>
                    <title/>
                    <table frame="all">
                        <title>Parameters</title>
                        <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
                                <entry>$serviceName</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>generally the name of the class which should respond to the request </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>$data</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>a model, some other format useful to the service </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>$options</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>options for request, e.g. to queue the data, process immediately etc </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                            <row>
                                <entry>$requester</entry>
                                <entry>
<para>who requested the service, or null if current logged in member </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                </formalpara>
                <formalpara><title>Returns: </title>

<para>mixed </para>
</formalpara>
</para>

